@natsir_pm
tags: natsir_major
title: **Major**: Forfeit our right to the Prime Ministership
unavailable-subtitle: Much of the party, including Sartono, oppose this. Afterall, why would we bring down Natsir only to bring him back again?
choose-if: masyumi_relation >= 100

cheater

@natsir_foreign
tags: natsir_major
title: **Major**: Forfeit the Ministry of Foreign Affairs
subtitle: The <span style="color: #000000;">**Masjumi**</span> hopes to bilaterally negotiate with the Netherlands regarding the Round Table Conference.
view-if: natsir_foreign_accepted = 0
on-arrival: natsir_foreign_accepted = 1
go-to: natsir_demands

We have forfeited the Ministry of Foreign Affairs. This is a major point of conjecture for the <span style="color: #000000;">**Masjumi**</span>, and secures us significant progress in negotiations.

@natsir_religion
tags: natsir_major
title: **Major**: Forfeit the Ministry of Religious Affairs
subtitle: The general consensus views the Ministry of Religious Affairs must be held by a religious party (Usually an <span style="color: #000000;">Islamic</span> one), and the <span style="color: #000000;">**Masjumi**</span> is an <span style="color: #000000;">Islamic</span>, religious party.
view-if: natsir_religion_accepted = 0
on-arrival: natsir_religion_accepted = 1
go-to: natsir_demands

We have forfeited the Ministry of Religious Affairs. This is a major point of conjecture for the <span style="color: #000000;">**Masjumi**</span>, and secures us significant progress in negotiations.

@natsir_r39
tags: natsir_minor
title: **Minor**: Pledge to not infringe upon regional councils formed on the basis of Government Regulation No. 39.
subtitle: Government Regulation No. 39 disproportionately benefits the <span style="color: #000000;">**Masjumi**</span> in regional councils, of course they don't want it to be changed.
view-if: natsir_r39_accepted = 0
on-arrival: natsir_r39_accepted = 1
go-to: natsir_demands

We have pledged not to reform the regional councils. This is a minor point of conjecture for the <span style="color: #000000;">**Masjumi**</span>, and secures us some progress in negotiations.

@natsir_finance
tags: natsir_minor
title: **Minor**: Forfeit the Ministry of Finance
subtitle: The economic successes of the Natsir cabinet has made the <span style="color: #000000;">**Masjumi**</span> to expect the Finance Ministry to be handed to them again.
view-if: natsir_finance_accepted = 0
on-arrival: natsir_finance_accepted = 1
go-to: natsir_demands

We have forfeited the Ministry of Finance. This is a minor point of conjecture for the <span style="color: #000000;">**Masjumi**</span>, and secures us some progress in negotiations.

@natsir_budget
tags: natsir_minor
title: **Minor**: Pledge to maintain budgetary surplus
subtitle: Financial stability is expected of any government, especially after the hyperinflation crisis.
view-if: natsir_budget_accepted = 0
on-arrival: natsir_budget_accepted = 1
go-to: natsir_demands

We have pledged to maintain budgetary surplus and not to enter a deficit. This is a minor point of conjecture for the <span style="color: #000000;">**Masjumi**</span>, and secures us some progress in negotiations.

